reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Standard packing cubes
reviews.reviewText: I love love love packing cubes. I know the jury is out on whether they actually save space when packing, but I can use these for so many things. Specifically for packing, the small ones aren't as useful for me, but they have good options on many sizes and kept things separated so I can easily toss things around without cluttering my bag. I also used some of these to just have a go-bag for quick travel and keeping things separate in drawers in my bathroom and linen closer. I only used the fluid/perfume holder once, but it worked as expected. I love the breathability and the low profile look of these specifically. Overall, really nice.
